14
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:15,550
Just 0.01 of a centimetre between us.

15
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,290
But 57 hours later...

16
00:02:19,370 --> 00:02:21,300
I fell in love with this woman.

17
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:25,630
Mrs. Chen? This is Qiwu.

18
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:29,300
Don't fetch May,
it's you I'm calling!

19
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:31,940
It's been a while, how are you?

20
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:39,090
I'm okay.
Yes, give May time to get over it.

21
00:02:39,150 --> 00:02:41,590
I'm sure she'll call me
when she's ready.

22
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:46,030
Please don't tell her I called.

23
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,430
You're going to a movie?

24
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,690
I won't keep you.
Is Mr. Chen there?

25
00:02:51,770 --> 00:02:53,890
[Car Horn Beeps]

26
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:58,300
Mr. Chen? This is Qiwu.

27
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:05,140
No, don't call May!
How's your cough?

28
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,720
You're going to the movie
with your wife?

29
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:11,270
I won't keep you then.

30
00:03:11,350 --> 00:03:13,340
Don't tell May I called!
Is her sister there?

31
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:16,820
No? Pass on my regards.

32
00:03:16,890 --> 00:03:19,990
[Qiwu Narrating]
We all have our habits.

33
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:22,590
- [Beeping]
- Mine is to wait here
for May after work.

34
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:27,230
The boss here says May looks like
a Japanese star.

35
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:29,270
She and I just split up.

36
