a Japanese star myself.

37
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:37,780
Message for account 3 68?

38
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:43,870
Call Ming? You mean May?

39
00:03:45,050 --> 00:03:51,080
Spell it!
" M-I -N-G" or " M-A-Y"?

40
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:54,260
Sure there's no mistake?

41
00:03:54,330 --> 00:03:57,320
Don't you know English?

42
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:06,440
Ming? I guess May asked you to call.

43
00:04:06,510 --> 00:04:09,700
Tell her not to worry, I'm fine.

44
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:12,340
I'm taking good care of myself.

45
00:04:12,410 --> 00:04:16,650
She can call me anytime she wants.

46
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,150
You don't need to mediate.

47
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:20,740
Huh?

48
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:22,760
She didn't?

49
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:25,090
So why are you paging me?

50
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,460
Jogging?

51
00:04:26,530 --> 00:04:28,460
Are you heartbroken again?

52
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,700
Then why go jogging?

53
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:35,100
