54
00:04:35,170 --> 00:04:38,160
Jogging is something private,
not something you do with an audience.

55
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,870
Forget it!

56
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,540
[Qiwu Narrating]
We're all unlucky in love sometimes.

57
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:49,210
When I am, I go jogging.

58
00:04:50,290 --> 00:04:53,350
The body loses water when you jog...

59
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:55,290
