161
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,970
"Undying love. "

162
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:59,800
No messages?

163
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:01,740
Sorry, no.

164
00:13:03,010 --> 00:13:04,640
Thanks anyway.

165
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:13,690
[Qiwu Narrating]
We split up on April Fool's Day.

166
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:17,490
So I decided to let the joke run
for a month.

167
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:23,500
Every day I buy a can of pineapple
with a sell-by date of May 1.

168
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:27,020
May loves pineapple...

169
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:30,160
and May 1 is my birthday.

170
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:34,970
If May hasn't changed her mind
by the time I've bought 30 cans...

171
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:38,240
then our love will also expire.

172
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,410
Sir, this can's life will expire
tomorrow.

173
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:46,580
I'll get you another one.

174
00:13:46,650 --> 00:13:48,020
No need.

175
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:54,750
The earliest flight tomorrow morning?

176
00:13:57,930 --> 00:13:59,990
I want to make a reservation.

177
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:05,810
Just one.

178
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,590
Have you seen these people?

179
00:14:29,660 --> 00:14:30,930
No.

180
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,590
Look carefully,
they're with their kids.

181
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:35,600
Can't help you.

182
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:57,950
[Men Chattering]

183
00:14:58,030 --> 00:15:00,290
- Have you ever seen them?
- No.

184
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:03,760
- Excuse me.
Have you ever seen these people?
- No.

185
00:15:03,830 --> 00:15:05,860
- These?
- No.

186
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:08,230
No?

187
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:10,240
No.

188
00:15:19,310 --> 00:15:21,710
- You really don't know?
- I've no idea where he is.

189
00:15:21,780 --> 00:15:23,910
But he's a friend of yours!

190
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:26,480
- No...
- Papa! Papa!

191
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:28,780
[Foreign Language]

192
00:15:36,230 --> 00:15:37,290
My daughter!

193
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:44,100
[Foreign Language]

194
00:15:44,170 --> 00:15:46,000
