257
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:02,920
In May's eyes...

258
00:22:02,980 --> 00:22:05,470
I'm no different
from a can of pineapple.

259
00:22:36,820 --> 00:22:40,050
Come on, try it!

260
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:42,750
Everyone says dogs are
a man's best friend.

261
00:22:43,890 --> 00:22:48,260
So how come mine won't share my grief?

262
