01:28:31,600 --> 01:28:35,230
 [Jukebox Song Ends]

1045
01:28:37,140 --> 01:28:39,700
I got to the restaurant a little early.

1046
01:28:39,780 --> 01:28:41,900
I half expected a flight delay.

1047
01:28:41,980 --> 01:28:43,500
So I got some loose change.

1048
01:28:57,660 --> 01:28:58,990
Coins, please.

1049
01:29:16,650 --> 01:29:21,110
Half an hour later,
I broke another $ 1 0 note.

1050
01:29:21,180 --> 01:29:22,910
Had the flight been cancelled?

1051
01:29:48,510 --> 01:29:50,480
She isn't coming.

1052
01:29:50,550 --> 01:29:53,010
She asked me to give you this.

1053
01:29:55,490 --> 01:29:58,010
Don't let it get you down,
though.

1054
01:29:58,090 --> 01:30:00,950
Try another girl.

1055
01:30:01,020 --> 01:30:05,760
May's nice.
She's coming back tomorrow.

1056
01:30:05,830 --> 01:30:06,990
Where is she?

1057
01:30:07,060 --> 01:30:12,000
She quit. Said she was
going to California.

1058
01:30:12,070 --> 01:30:13,930
Nothing else.

1059
01:30:14,000 --> 01:30:15,060
Thanks.

1060
01:30:19,040 --> 01:30:20,670
[No. 633 Narrating]
I didn't open the letter.

1061
01:30:22,110 --> 01:30:25,170
Some things need time
to sink in.

1062
01:30:25,250 --> 01:30:27,910
Once the snack bar manager
had gone...

1063
01:30:27,980 --> 01:30:30,890
I started talking
to the beer bottles.

1064
01:30:30,950 --> 01:30:33,180
Disappointed?

1065
01:30:33,260 --> 01:30:35,420
Not really.

1066
01:30:35,490 --> 01:30:39,430
Go home and sleep.
She's not coming.

1067
01:30:50,840 --> 01:30:52,810
Actually, she did go
to California that evening.

1068
01:30:52,880 --> 01:30:55,540
But it was the other one.

1069
01:30:55,610 --> 01:30:58,380
We were in
different Califrornias...

1070
01:30:58,450 --> 01:31:00,510
with a 15 hour time difference
between us.

1071
01:31:02,350 --> 01:31:04,950
It must be 11:00 a.m.
in California, USA.

1072
01:31:06,960 --> 01:31:09,220
I wonder if she'll remember
our 8:00 p.m date here.

1073
01:31:24,840 --> 01:31:26,780
[Woman Speaks Chinese]

1074
01:31:28,640 --> 01:31:30,370
What a coincidence.

1075
01:31:32,820 --> 01:31:35,340
Are you off duty tonight?

1076
01:31:35,420 --> 01:31:36,350
Yes.

1077
01:31:38,450 --> 01:31:40,390
How are you?

1078
01:31:40,460 --> 01:31:42,860
No change. And you?

1079
01:31:42,930 --> 01:31:45,520
Not bad.

1080
01:31:45,600 --> 01:31:47,360
Alone?

1081
01:31:47,430 --> 01:31:48,900
No, my friend's waiting.

1082
01:31:52,300 --> 01:31:53,730
Your type.

1083
01:31:54,900 --> 01:31:57,740
I still have some of your stuff.

1084
01:31:57,810 --> 01:31:59,400
Will you pick it up sometime?

1085
01:31:59,480 --> 01:32:02,840
Wouldn't want it anymore.
Throw it away.

1086
01:32:05,280 --> 01:32:05,870
Okay.

1087
01:32:05,950 --> 01:32:08,210
[Horn Honks]

1088
01:32:08,280 --> 01:32:10,450
[Motorcycle Engine Starts]

1089
01:32:10,520 --> 01:32:12,350
I have to rush.

1090
01:32:12,420 --> 01:32:14,820
[Engine Revving]

1091
01:32:14,890 --> 01:32:17,120
I still think
you look better in uniform.

1092
01:32:18,760 --> 01:32:19,490
So do you.

1093
01:32:19,560 --> 01:32:21,330
- Bye-bye.
- Bye.

1094
01:32:23,600 --> 01:32:25,260
Hey, you haven't paid!

1095
01:32:25,330 --> 01:32:27,000
You pay for me!

1096
01:32:31,910 --> 01:32:36,240
[Engine Revs, Accelerates]

1097
01:32:57,930 --> 01:33:00,230
- How much is it?
- $262, please.

1098
01:33:08,880 --> 01:33:10,810
[Chinese]

1099
01:34:41,970 --> 01:34:44,000
[No. 633 Narrating]
The letter turned out to be
a boarding pass...

1100
01:34:44,070 --> 01:34:46,700
postdated one year later.

1101
01:34:46,780 --> 01:34:49,840
I couldn't make out
the destination.

1102
01:35:02,960 --> 01:35:05,480
[Faye Narrating]
I did go to the restaurant that evening.

1103
01:35:05,560 --> 01:35:09,620
I knew it would get crowded
so I was there at 7:1 5.

1104
01:35:09,700 --> 01:35:11,760
It poured with rain outside.

1105
01:35:11,830 --> 01:35:15,630
I watched it fall
through the window.

1106
01:35:17,440 --> 01:35:19,670
And I urgently needed to know
if the other California...

1107
01:35:19,740 --> 01:35:21,180
was warm and sunny.

1108
01:35:21,240 --> 01:35:23,070
I decided to give myself
one year.

1109
01:35:25,280 --> 01:35:28,940
Tonight it's raining
as hard as it was then.

1110
01:35:29,020 --> 01:35:30,880
Looking out this window...

1111
01:35:30,950 --> 01:35:32,610
I have only one person
in my thoughts.

1112
01:35:34,720 --> 01:35:36,690
I wonder if he ever
opened my letter.

1113
01:36:05,650 --> 01:36:10,090
-  All the leaves are brown 
-  All the leaves are brown 

1114
01:36:10,160 --> 01:36:14,820
-  And the sky is Gray 
-  And the sky is Gray 

1115
01:36:14,900 --> 01:36:18,660
-  I've been for a walk 
-  I've been for a walk 

1116
01:36:18,730 --> 01:36:23,430
-  On a winter's day 
-  On a winter's day 

1117
01:36:23,510 --> 01:36:27,240
-  I'd be safe and warm 
-  I'd be safe and warm 

1118
01:36:27,310 --> 01:36:32,250
-  If I was in L.A. 
-  If I was in L.A. 

1119
01:36:32,310 --> 01:36:35,180
 California dreaming

1120
01:36:35,250 --> 01:36:36,310
What are you doing here?

1121
01:36:36,390 --> 01:36:39,010
 On such a winter's day 

1122
01:36:39,090 --> 01:36:40,250
What are you doing here?

1123
01:36:40,320 --> 01:36:43,760
 [Continues, Loud]

1124
01:36:44,990 --> 01:36:46,020
Can that be you?

1125
01:36:46,100 --> 01:36:49,090
What are you doing here?

1126
01:36:49,170 --> 01:36:50,530
Renovating.

1127
01:36:50,600 --> 01:36:51,530
Renovating?

1128
01:36:53,600 --> 01:36:55,070
Where's my cousin?

1129
01:36:55,140 --> 01:36:57,770
He opened a karaoke bar.

1130
01:36:59,880 --> 01:37:02,040
Said he needed a change.

1131
01:37:02,110 --> 01:37:04,440
So I took over here.
Didn't he tell you?

1132
01:37:05,950 --> 01:37:08,850
I haven't seen him.

1133
01:37:08,920 --> 01:37:12,380
He has great business sense.

1134
01:37:12,450 --> 01:37:14,890
First he sold me
fish and chips...

1135
01:37:14,960 --> 01:37:16,720
then the whole thing.

1136
01:37:16,790 --> 01:37:18,280
What?

1137
01:37:18,360 --> 01:37:20,160
I said, he has
great business sense!

1138
01:37:26,870 --> 01:37:29,100
When did you
get into this music?

1139
01:37:31,540 --> 01:37:33,200
It takes time
to get used to things.

1140
01:37:36,150 --> 01:37:38,140
Did you go to California?
Was it fun?

1141
01:37:38,210 --> 01:37:40,150
Huh?

1142
01:37:43,290 --> 01:37:46,220
 [Volume Decreases,
Shuts Off]

1143
01:37:48,290 --> 01:37:50,820
Nothing special.

1144
01:37:51,490 --> 01:37:54,430
[Chinese]

1145
01:38:03,640 --> 01:38:05,230
You look good in uniform.

1146
01:38:07,310 --> 01:38:09,780
You look nice like that too.

1147
01:38:09,850 --> 01:38:12,180
Fancy a bite to eat?

1148
01:38:12,250 --> 01:38:16,810
No, I fly out
very early tomorrow.

1149
01:38:19,490 --> 01:38:21,850
When will you get back?

1150
01:38:21,920 --> 01:38:23,590
My grand opening
is two days away.

1151
01:38:26,430 --> 01:38:30,130
Don't know.
This might be a long trip.

1152
01:38:34,670 --> 01:38:37,430
Write to me when you reach
wherever it is.

1153
01:38:40,140 --> 01:38:42,270
Would you read it if I did?

1154
01:38:42,340 --> 01:38:44,570
Hey.

1155
01:38:44,650 --> 01:38:46,710
One thing I must ask you.

1156
01:38:57,630 --> 01:38:59,560
Would you let
a person on board...

1157
01:38:59,630 --> 01:39:01,620
with a boarding pass like this?

1158
01:39:06,940 --> 01:39:10,370
It's dated today,
but it got blurred in the rain.

1159
01:39:10,440 --> 01:39:14,840
I don't know
where it's taking me. Do you?

1160
01:39:17,480 --> 01:39:21,880
No idea,
but I'll give you another.

1161
01:39:26,790 --> 01:39:27,720
Great.

1162
01:39:39,070 --> 01:39:40,830
Where do you want to go?

1163
01:39:41,900 --> 01:39:44,840
Wherever you want to take me.

1164
01:40:23,050 --> 01:40:26,810
 [Woman Singing In Chinese]

1165
01:41:22,400 --> 01:41:25,840
 [Singing Continues]

